description:
<!--StartFragment-->

Eagles Wings Productions Minstrel Asheck with visuals based on her life story ministers and encourages followers of the Master to always be appreciative of the Lord Jesus Christ and the unconditional love he grants to us all. 

Drawn from excerpts such as Psalms 34: 1-3 and Psalms 138: 1-2, this melodious piece will uplift your spirit and remind you to always thank God for everything he has done, is doing and will do. 

Whoever takes the time to watch this video and listen to every word of the song would delve into thanksgiving as we know that the Lord we serve is a wonderful and powerful one and must be appreciated. God bless you!!

<!--EndFragment-->
